title: Match not showing
body: Hello, I recently played a Normal PvP match and I notced that it doesnt show in my Match History. But it does on the other players' that I was with in that game. Got any idea how I can fix that? Thanks

replies.body: Could have been some delays in updating match history on your account.  Are you still not seeing the game? If so, can you provide some more info about the game (Who you were playing, if you won, etc.) so I can look into it a little more?
